  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>For breakfast you will fuel up on delicious food, sustainably sourced. The hot and cold buffet is open until 10am every day in the cosy indoor restaurant. </p>
<p>In the evening, you can visit the MADly restaurant at an additional cost, serving incredible cuisine from all around the world until 9:30pm. You will be spoilt for choice with an extensive menu including Japanese tataki, Swiss grilled cheese, Italian pizzas and so much more. </p>
<p>The bar and terrace are fantastic for maximising your time in the great outdoors, with comfortable seating and breath-taking mountain views. Grab a specially crafted local cocktail, beer or wine and unwind as the sun sets.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
